!attack import - name: Blade of the Magister, Radiant Light
  automation:
    - type: target
      target: each 
      effects:
        - type: attack
          hit:
            - type: damage
              damage: 1d8 + {wisdomMod + 3} [magical piercing] + 1d6 [magical radiant]
              overheal: false
          miss: []
          attackBonus: wisdomMod + proficiencyBonus + 3
    - type: text
      text: Granted to a contributer to the continent of Faeyis and its Mistress, the Blade of the Magister is a weapon reserved for a champion of Mystra, Goddess of All Magic.  It can strike with either light or darkness as the whims of the wielder desire.  On a critical hit, the wielder rolls 1d20 and restores a spell slot of the appropriate level or lower (1-3 1st, 4-6 2nd, 7-10 3rd, 11-13 4th, 14-15 5th, 16-17 6th, 18 7th, 19 8th, 20 9th).  If no spell slot of that level or lower is available, the wielder can instead select a number of enemies with 30 ft equal to their proficiency bonus to target with Inflict Wounds or a number of allies within 30 ft equal to their proficiency bonus to target with Mass Cure Wounds without expending a spell slot.
  _v: 2

